OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA largely dry day with bright
OL,6,For sunny spells, the odd isolated
OL,7,Fshower possible in the morning.
OL,8,FTurning cloudier over Orkney by the
OL,9,Fend of the afternoon. Fresh
OL,10,Fsouthwesterly winds turning southerly.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCloudy with heavy rain across
OL,13,FOrkney this evening and strong winds.
OL,14,FShetland starts drier with bright
OL,15,Fspells, then cloud thickens as rain
OL,16,Farrives overnight, becoming patchy
OL,17,Flater for all areas.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
