OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FCloudy start with rain over
OL,6,FOrkney spreading north to reach
OL,7,FShetland by the afternoon. Bright
OL,8,Fspells and a few showers over Orkney
OL,9,Fonce rain clears. Strong westerly
OL,10,Fwinds for Orkney.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FA
OL,13,Fcloudy start with showers on Saturday
OL,14,Fbefore turning drier with bright
OL,15,Fspells developing. Sunday and Monday
OL,16,Fwill be dry with sunny spells. Breezy
OL,17,FSaturday then winds easing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
